author: The Wall Street Journal
description:
Former Microsoft CEO and philanthropist Bill Gates spoke to WSJ about a recent meeting with Donald Trump, Elon Musk’s DOGE, U.S.-China relations and his upcoming book, “Source Code,” in which he reveals new details about his childhood. In the wide-ranging interview, Gates also discusses RFK Jr., supporting Kamala Harris’s campaign and more.
